<text><body>
<cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">諸般偈讚門</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">放生</cb:mulu>
<lb ed="X" n="0022b12"/><milestone unit="juan" n="6"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0022b13"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0022b14"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0022b15"/><lb ed="R114" n="0043a12"/><cb:juan fun="open" n="006"><cb:mulu type="卷" n="6"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead>高峰龍泉院因師集賢語錄卷之六</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="X" n="0022b16"/><lb ed="R114" n="0043a13"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0022b17"/><lb ed="R114" n="0043a14"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">薦亡偈讚門</cb:mulu><head>薦亡偈讚門</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0022b18"/><lb ed="R114" n="0043a15"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">薦亡通用</cb:mulu><head>薦亡通用</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0022b19"/><lb ed="R114" n="0043a16"/><lg xml:id="lgX65p0022b1901"><l>人生薤露固難延</l><l>去若孤舟逐逝川</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0022b20"/><lb ed="R114" n="0043a17"/><l>百歲光陰今<anchor xml:id="beg_2b" type="cb-app"/>已<anchor xml:id="end_2b"/>矣</l><l>九泉冥路太茫然</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0022b21"/><lb ed="R114" n="0043a18"/><l>筵堆玉饌天厨供</l><l>香爇金爐海岸煙</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0022b22"/><lb ed="R114" n="0043b01"/><l>好聽良因功德力</l><l>迢迢直造率陀天</l></lg>
<lb ed="X" n="0022b23"/><lb ed="R114" n="0043b02"/><p xml:id="pX65p0022b2301" rend="margin-left:4em">又</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0022b24"/><lb ed="R114" n="0043b03"/><lg xml:id="lgX65p0022b2401"><l>積功累德性溫溫</l><l>庭玉森然列子孫</l>
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X65.1277.0022c" n="0022c"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0022c01"/><lb ed="R114" n="0043b04"/><l>未滿百年身色夢</l><l><anchor xml:id="beg_2c" type="cb-app"/>已<anchor xml:id="end_2c"/>歸一路涅槃門</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0022c02"/><lb ed="R114" n="0043b05"/><l>燈燃七級資冥福</l><l>經演三題悼去魂</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0022c03"/><lb ed="R114" n="0043b06"/><l>彈指直趍無垢界</l><l>超凡入聖契真源</l></lg>
<lb ed="X" n="0022c04"/><lb ed="R114" n="0043b07"/><p xml:id="pX65p0022c0401" rend="margin-left:4em">又</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0022c05"/><lb ed="R114" n="0043b08"/><lg xml:id="lgX65p0022c0501"><l>青天明月尚虧圓</l><l>人世那能有十全</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0022c06"/><lb ed="R114" n="0043b09"/><l>本謂百年膺五福</l><l>何期一旦返重泉</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0022c07"/><lb ed="R114" n="0043b10"/><l>滿堂兒女肝腸斷</l><l>合族親姻涕淚漣</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0022c08"/><lb ed="R114" n="0043b11"/><l>仰冀尊魂承佛力</l><l>白毫光裏禮金仙</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0022c09"/><lb ed="R114" n="0043b12"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">婦人</cb:mulu><head>婦人</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0022c10"/><lb ed="R114" n="0043b13"/><lg xml:id="lgX65p0022c1001"><l>夫人淑德絕纖瑕</l><l>歸配于門積善家</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0022c11"/><lb ed="R114" n="0043b14"/><l>列砌芝蘭森後裔</l><l>滿堂金玉足生涯</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0022c12"/><lb ed="R114" n="0043b15"/><l>本期壽等龜齡永</l><l>豈謂魂隨蝶夢賖</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0022c13"/><lb ed="R114" n="0043b16"/><l>拜佛燃灯資托化</l><l>從今世世會龍華</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0022c14"/><lb ed="R114" n="0043b17"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">老人</cb:mulu><head>老人</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0022c15"/><lb ed="R114" n="0043b18"/><lg xml:id="lgX65p0022c1501"><l>康寧富壽獨兼全</l><l>堪作人間不老仙</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0022c16"/><lb ed="R114" n="0044a01"/><l>子舍騰芳咸起敬</l><l>孫枝競秀總推賢</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0022c17"/><lb ed="R114" n="0044a02"/><l><anchor xml:id="beg_2d" type="cb-app"/>已<anchor xml:id="end_2d"/>看一鴞摩雲表</l><l>未覩双龍化眼前</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0022c18"/><lb ed="R114" n="0044a03"/><l>憑仗佛慈伸薦<g ref="#CB15072">󳫠</g></l><l>英魂騰踏率陀天</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0022c19"/><lb ed="R114" n="0044a04"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">薦公</cb:mulu><head>薦公</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0022c20"/><lb ed="R114" n="0044a05"/><lg xml:id="lgX65p0022c2001"><l>興家<g ref="#CB16555">󴂫</g>業事堪悲</l><l>西沒東升似落暉</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0022c21"/><lb ed="R114" n="0044a06"/><l>逝魄雲程今有路</l><l>孝孫雨淚痛沾衣</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0022c22"/><lb ed="R114" n="0044a07"/><l>雖言高壽元無憾</l><l>爭奈卑懷遽失依</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0022c23"/><lb ed="R114" n="0044a08"/><l>我佛慈悲求引接</l><l>好隨隻履共西歸</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0022c24"/><lb ed="R114" n="0044a09"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">薦婆</cb:mulu><head>薦婆</head>
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X65.1277.0023a" n="0023a"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0023a01"/><lb ed="R114" n="0044a10"/><lg xml:id="lgX65p0023a0101"><l>夫人懿德配于門</l><l>勤儉宜家眾所尊</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0023a02"/><lb ed="R114" n="0044a11"/><l>舉目雖云無一子</l><l>承顏幸喜有諸孫</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0023a03"/><lb ed="R114" n="0044a12"/><l>本期壽等靈椿固</l><l>豈意身隨逝水奔</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0023a04"/><lb ed="R114" n="0044a13"/><l>今夜孝孫崇妙果</l><l>願隨我佛步天閽</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0023a05"/><lb ed="R114" n="0044a14"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">父母</cb:mulu><head>父母</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0023a06"/><lb ed="R114" n="0044a15"/><lg xml:id="lgX65p0023a0601"><l>藥師灌頂妙難論</l><l>仰仗慈悲薦二魂</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0023a07"/><lb ed="R114" n="0044a16"/><l>法雨洒除冤業障</l><l>惠燈照破生死門</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0023a08"/><lb ed="R114" n="0044a17"/><l>當年<anchor xml:id="beg_2e" type="cb-app"/>已<anchor xml:id="end_2e"/>荷劬勞德</l><l>是夜難酬怙恃恩</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0023a09"/><lb ed="R114" n="0044a18"/><l>伏願双親乘妙善</l><l>蓮臺上品禮慈尊</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0023a10"/><lb ed="R114" n="0044b01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">薦父</cb:mulu><head>薦父</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0023a11"/><lb ed="R114" n="0044b02"/><lg xml:id="lgX65p0023a1101"><l>先君一夢熟黃粱</l><l>霧慘雲愁去路茫</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0023a12"/><lb ed="R114" n="0044b03"/><l>對景<anchor xml:id="beg_2f" type="cb-app"/>已<anchor xml:id="end_2f"/>枯双淚眼</l><l>臨風空結九回腸</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0023a13"/><lb ed="R114" n="0044b04"/><l>文章千古留清世</l><l>魂魄今宵返故鄉</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0023a14"/><lb ed="R114" n="0044b05"/><l>陟岵興嗟崇妙果</l><l>願隨我佛往西方</l></lg>
<lb ed="X" n="0023a15"/><lb ed="R114" n="0044b06"/><p xml:id="pX65p0023a1501" rend="margin-left:4em">又</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0023a16"/><lb ed="R114" n="0044b07"/><lg xml:id="lgX65p0023a1601"><l>愁雲黯黯淚盈腮</l><l>追憶先君幾七來</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0023a17"/><lb ed="R114" n="0044b08"/><l>陟岵興嗟人不見</l><l>蓼義託詠事堪哀</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0023a18"/><lb ed="R114" n="0044b09"/><l>清華堂上知何往</l><l>縞素帷中喚不回</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0023a19"/><lb ed="R114" n="0044b10"/><l>唯仗今宵功德力</l><l>慈悲接引步蓮臺</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0023a20"/><lb ed="R114" n="0044b11"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">薦母</cb:mulu><head>薦母</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0023a21"/><lb ed="R114" n="0044b12"/><lg xml:id="lgX65p0023a2101"><l>斷機昔日卜芳鄰</l><l>一別音容不可尋</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0023a22"/><lb ed="R114" n="0044b13"/><l>忍見稻粱収畎畝</l><l>愁聞楓葉落平林</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0023a23"/><lb ed="R114" n="0044b14"/><l>望雲幾度思親面</l><l>泣笋無因表孝心</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0023a24"/><lb ed="R114" n="0044b15"/><l>特設伊蒲伸薦果</l><l>大千佛國震雷音</l></lg>
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X65.1277.0023b" n="0023b"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0023b01"/><lb ed="R114" n="0044b16"/><p xml:id="pX65p0023b0101" rend="margin-left:4em">又</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0023b02"/><lb ed="R114" n="0044b17"/><lg xml:id="lgX65p0023b0201"><l>三年泣血淚霑紅</l><l>鞠育還如一夢中</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0023b03"/><lb ed="R114" n="0044b18"/><l>輟社當年懷舊恨</l><l>感鄰今日有遺風</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0023b04"/><lb ed="R114" n="0045a01"/><l>本期椿筭綿綿遠</l><l>豈謂萱堂寂寂空</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0023b05"/><lb ed="R114" n="0045a02"/><l>願假目連行孝力</l><l>慈親從此往天宮</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0023b06"/><lb ed="R114" n="0045a03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">母小祥</cb:mulu><head>母小祥</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0023b07"/><lb ed="R114" n="0045a04"/><lg xml:id="lgX65p0023b0701"><l>積功累行播三從</l><l>順色承顏孝道終</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0023b08"/><lb ed="R114" n="0045a05"/><l>萱草一從凋晚景</l><l>桃花重見笑春風</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0023b09"/><lb ed="R114" n="0045a06"/><l>白雲望斷關山隔</l><l>青鳥歸無信息通</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0023b10"/><lb ed="R114" n="0045a07"/><l>拜佛修因酬罔極</l><l>騰身高躡九蓮宮</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0023b11"/><lb ed="R114" n="0045a08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">母大祥</cb:mulu><head>母大祥</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0023b12"/><lb ed="R114" n="0045a09"/><lg xml:id="lgX65p0023b1201"><l>先親一夢返蓬萊</l><l>逝魄滔滔去不回</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0023b13"/><lb ed="R114" n="0045a10"/><l>先逐白雲歸洞府</l><l>却隨青鳥過瑤臺</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0023b14"/><lb ed="R114" n="0045a11"/><l>一從諼草凋零別</l><l>三見梅英漏泄開</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0023b15"/><lb ed="R114" n="0045a12"/><l>哀子崇因伸孝道</l><l>早隨彌勒下生來</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0023b16"/><lb ed="R114" n="0045a13"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">薦夫</cb:mulu><head>薦夫</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0023b17"/><lb ed="R114" n="0045a14"/><lg xml:id="lgX65p0023b1701"><l>千行血淚欲崩城</l><l>不見當年結髮人</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0023b18"/><lb ed="R114" n="0045a15"/><l>座上難聞新笑語</l><l>筆端空寫舊精神</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0023b19"/><lb ed="R114" n="0045a16"/><l>鸞飛鏡裏嗟孤影</l><l>鳳立釵頭恨隻身</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0023b20"/><lb ed="R114" n="0045a17"/><l>拜佛薰修功莫大</l><l>回頭業鏡絕纖塵</l></lg>
<lb ed="X" n="0023b21"/><lb ed="R114" n="0045a18"/><p xml:id="pX65p0023b2101" rend="margin-left:4em">又</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0023b22"/><lb ed="R114" n="0045b01"/><lg xml:id="lgX65p0023b2201"><l>本期偕老百年中</l><l>豈謂夫天遽壽終</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0023b23"/><lb ed="R114" n="0045b02"/><l>昔日齊眉人不在</l><l>今朝結髮事成空</l>
