<lb ed="X" n="0026c09"/><lb ed="R114" n="0051b12"/><l>生前情識双垂淚</l><l>熟底親知寸斷腸</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0026c10"/><lb ed="R114" n="0051b13"/><l>五濁漏身乘薦悼</l><l>白毫光裏禮醫王</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0026c11"/><lb ed="R114" n="0051b14"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">縊死</cb:mulu><head>縊死</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0026c12"/><lb ed="R114" n="0051b15"/><lg xml:id="lgX65p0026c1201"><l>生平東注太英雄</l><l>視死還同一夢中</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0026c13"/><lb ed="R114" n="0051b16"/><l>步步那能踏實地</l><l>頭頭直欲撞虗空</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0026c14"/><lb ed="R114" n="0051b17"/><l>化身直入虗無境</l><l>撒手還歸快樂宮</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0026c15"/><lb ed="R114" n="0051b18"/><l>惟願佛慈垂接引</l><l>綵雲捧足禮金容</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0026c16"/><lb ed="R114" n="0052a01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">焚死</cb:mulu><head>焚死</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0026c17"/><lb ed="R114" n="0052a02"/><lg xml:id="lgX65p0026c1701"><l>夜深方鎻六窻猴</l><l>人在莊周夢裏遊</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0026c18"/><lb ed="R114" n="0052a03"/><l>恍惚此身歸大幻</l><l>倉皇無計下層樓</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0026c19"/><lb ed="R114" n="0052a04"/><l>風回火轉三更後</l><l>煙滅<g ref="#CB01926">󰞆</g>飛萬事休</l>
<lb ed="X" n="0026c20"/><lb ed="R114" n="0052a05"/><l>子母不須頻抱恨</l><l>火光三昧任遨遊</l></lg></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0026c21"/><lb ed="R114" n="0052a06"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0026c22"/><lb ed="R114" n="0052a07"/><cb:juan fun="close" n="006"><cb:jhead>高峰龍泉院因師集賢語錄卷之六</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
</body>
